<!--<h4>First Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>© svasti śrīmatu yādavanārāyaṇaṁ pratāpabhujabaḷa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>cakravartti siṁhaṇadēva<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>riśada 19 byuyasa<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>vatsarada bhādra
<lb n="3" break="no"/>pada su <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1 <unclear>lu</unclear> nuṟuṁbāḍa sattaḷigenāḍa samasta prabhu gā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>muṁḍagaḷu samasta parivāravuṁ neradu halugeṟeya be
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḷugaliya sīmāsamma<unclear>ṁ</unclear>dhakke kāḷegavādali Antaravaḷḷiya baḍagi gō
<lb n="6" break="no"/>mōjana maga rāmōja taḷutiṟidu meṟadu suralō
<lb n="7" break="no"/>kaprāptanāda ma<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>gaḷa mahāśrī śrī
</p>

